page.title: 08Colemere SSSI-Bird Survey
page.content: Water and Wetland Birds - species seen during the past year- Resident: Great Crested Grebe, Grey Heron, Mute Swan, Canada Goose, Barnacle Goose, Mallard, Tufted Duck, Moorhen, Coot. Winter Visitors: Wigeon, Shoveller, Pochard, Goldeneye, White-Fronted Goose, Cormorant. Other Visitors: Black Tern, Common Sandpiper, Yellow Wagtail, Pied Wagtail, Snipe, Black-Headed Gull, Common Gull, Ruddy Duck. Woodland Birds: Tits-Great, Long-Tail, Blue, Marsh, Willow. Woodpeckers-Green, Great Spotted, Lesser Spotted. Black Cap. Whitethroat. Chiff Chaff. Willow Warbler. Nuthatch. Treecreeper. Cuckoo. Tawny Owl. Pheasant. Goldcrest. Wren. Mistle Thrust. Song Thrush. Blackbird. Jay. Magpie.
